      <title>印度小盘股价值 800 亿美元的暴跌发出警告信号</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/an-80-billion-crash-in-india-s-small-caps-flashes-warning-signs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[小盘股的大幅调整预示着整个印度市场的风险偏好下降，印度市场在经历了多年的上涨之后，目前在亚太地区表现不佳。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/an-80-billion-crash-in-india-s-small-caps-flashes-warning-signs</guid>
