    <item>
      <title>金瑞股份首席执行官表示，中国市场正处于“难以置信的切入点”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-14/china-market-at-incredible-entry-point-kraneshares-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[KraneShares 创始人兼首席执行官 Jonathan Krane 讨论了中国市场的前景。 KraneShares 是一家资产管理公司，为全球投资者提供专注于中国和气候的交易所交易基金。克兰在“彭博社：中国秀”上发表讲话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-14/china-market-at-incredible-entry-point-kraneshares-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 02:17:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国铜冶炼厂誓言在费用暴跌后控制产能</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/copper-marches-toward-9-000-a-ton-as-global-market-tightens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的铜冶炼厂承诺控制产能，同时停止协调减产，因为该行业对全球精矿市场的紧缩做出了反应，导致加工费降至几乎为零。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/copper-marches-toward-9-000-a-ton-as-global-market-tightens</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 02:14:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对今年日元上涨的厚望让位于小幅上涨的言论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/high-hopes-for-yen-rally-this-year-give-way-to-talk-of-slim-gain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对日元今年跑赢其他货币的预期几乎已经消失，策略师目前预测日元汇率到 2024 年年底的涨幅将比年初的幅度小几个百分点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/high-hopes-for-yen-rally-this-year-give-way-to-talk-of-slim-gain</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 01:48:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
